{
  "stem": "26983.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was a child, and it was a gifted child.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't yet art.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, as I told you, my first time I sold something was for a very high price-- a half loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But, as I was a gifted child, I got all the encouragement through Fredy Hirsch, through Jacob Edelstein.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of-- through them, I could meet all the artists who supported me with pencils, paper, and critique and teaching.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was just drawing what I found interesting.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, of course, I was looking over the shoulders-- which was fascinating for me, to see a real artist.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when you are 13 and 1/2 or something like that, to see an artist at work, or to be even in his atelier, that was a kind of very exciting thing.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our teacher from Mahrisch Ostrau, who was the head teacher of the class-- headmaster of our class-- was Leopold Lowinger.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I knew him very well, and his son was also my good friend.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And his wife was related to Sigmund Freud.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sigmund Freud.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She came from Moravia-- Freud was born in Moravia, not far from Mahrisch Ostrau.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was a librarian in Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Theresienstadt was a library-- a lending library.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By the way, later on I will show you a book.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have still a book, the Bible, with the stamp Zentral Ghetto Bucherei.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's a story.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I got it after the war, of course.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But that is from this library.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyhow, this teacher was there in this library.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember, once I went to the [NON-ENGLISH] Kaserne, and I-- and there were a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
